## What to do now — step by step:

1. Go to your GitHub repo: `https://github.com/xaynwolfe-beep/aria`
2. Click on `api/chat.js` → click the **pencil (edit) icon** → select all → delete everything → paste the new `api/chat.js` code above → click **Commit changes**
3. Do the same for `api/auth/callback.js`
4. Do the same for `package.json`
5. Go to Vercel dashboard → wait for auto-deploy to finish (green "Ready")
6. Open your app, **logout**, then **sign in again with Google**
7. Try: *"Summarize my recent emails"*

The AI should now reply with your **real emails and calendar events**.

